description:
In this lesson I demonstrate an ear training exercise that Mick Goodrick showed some years ago. 

Triad Pairs-"3 Volume Package" is now available at:

www.triadpairs.com
 
This package includes:

3 books and 2 video workshops (122 minutes worth of video in total):

 1) "A Guide to Developing a Chromatic Approach"

 2) Triad Pairs-"The First Step"

 3) Triad Pairs-"Harmonic Foundations"

​4) 2 additional Video Workshops

​5)A passcode to a private study group and access to a free forthcoming live workshop.

​*This package will be available until the release of Triad Pairs-"A Chromatic Approach"
